---
import DocsLayout from '../../../layouts/DocsLayout.astro';
import ComponentDocLayout from '../../../components/ComponentDocLayout.astro';
const toc = [
  { href: '#overview', label: 'Overview', active: true },
  { href: '#anatomy', label: 'Anatomy' },
  { href: '#examples', label: 'Examples' },
  { href: '#html', label: 'HTML' }
];
---
<DocsLayout title="Cards" description="Dokumentasi card piceUI" section="components">
  <ComponentDocLayout active="card" title="Card" description="Card adalah container konten untuk panel, list item, pricing box, dan section dashboard." toc={toc}>
    <Fragment slot="hero-preview"><div class="card"><div class="card-header">Sample</div><div class="card-body">Content card</div></div></Fragment>

    <section id="overview" class="card mt-8 max-w-4xl"><div class="card-header">Overview</div><div class="card-body"><p>Card memakai token surface, border, radius, shadow, dan content color. Ini membuat card siap mengikuti tema tanpa mengganti markup.</p></div></section>

    <section id="anatomy" class="card mt-6 max-w-4xl"><div class="card-header">Anatomy</div><div class="card-body overflow-x-auto p-0"><table class="w-full text-left text-sm"><tbody class="divide-y divide-neutral-200 dark:divide-neutral-700"><tr><td class="px-6 py-4 font-mono">card</td><td class="px-6 py-4">Wrapper surface dengan border, radius, dan shadow.</td></tr><tr><td class="px-6 py-4 font-mono">card-header</td><td class="px-6 py-4">Area judul atau toolbar atas.</td></tr><tr><td class="px-6 py-4 font-mono">card-body</td><td class="px-6 py-4">Area konten utama.</td></tr><tr><td class="px-6 py-4 font-mono">card-footer</td><td class="px-6 py-4">Area aksi atau meta bawah.</td></tr></tbody></table></div></section>

    <section id="examples" class="mt-6 grid max-w-4xl gap-6 lg:grid-cols-2"><div class="card"><div class="card-header">Project Summary</div><div class="card-body">Ini card dengan header dan body.</div><div class="card-footer"><button class="btn btn-primary btn-sm">Open</button></div></div><div class="card"><div class="card-body"><span class="badge badge-success">Active</span><h2 class="mt-3 text-xl font-semibold">Simple Card</h2><p class="mt-2 text-neutral-600 dark:text-neutral-300">Card juga bisa hanya memakai body.</p></div></div></section>
    <section id="html" class="card mt-6 max-w-4xl"><div class="card-header">HTML</div><div class="card-body"><pre class="overflow-auto rounded bg-neutral-900 p-4 text-sm text-neutral-100"><code>&lt;div class="card"&gt;
  &lt;div class="card-header"&gt;Title&lt;/div&gt;
  &lt;div class="card-body"&gt;Content&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;</code></pre></div></section>
  </ComponentDocLayout>
</DocsLayout>
